---
source: crates/biome_formatter_test/src/snapshot_builder.rs
info: scss/expression/function-argument-comments.scss
---

# Input

```scss
.comments{
line:outerFunctionWithAnExtremelyLongName(1,
// line comment
nestedFunctionWithAnExtremelyLongName(firstArgumentWithLongName,secondArgumentWithLongName,thirdArgumentWithLongName));
block:outerFunctionWithAnExtremelyLongName(1,
/* block comment */
nestedFunctionWithAnExtremelyLongName(firstArgumentWithLongName,secondArgumentWithLongName,thirdArgumentWithLongName));
binary:fn(1,
// binary comment
veryLongArgumentName + anotherVeryLongArgumentName + thirdVeryLongArgumentName);
list:fn(1,
// list comment
firstVeryLongListItem secondVeryLongListItem thirdVeryLongListItem fourthVeryLongListItem);
}

```


# Formatted

```scss
.comments {
	line: outerFunctionWithAnExtremelyLongName(
		1,
		// line comment
		nestedFunctionWithAnExtremelyLongName(
				firstArgumentWithLongName,
				secondArgumentWithLongName,
				thirdArgumentWithLongName
			)
	);
	block: outerFunctionWithAnExtremelyLongName(
		1,
		/* block comment */
		nestedFunctionWithAnExtremelyLongName(
				firstArgumentWithLongName,
				secondArgumentWithLongName,
				thirdArgumentWithLongName
			)
	);
	binary: fn(
		1,
		// binary comment
		veryLongArgumentName + anotherVeryLongArgumentName +
			thirdVeryLongArgumentName
	);
	list: fn(
		1,
		// list comment
		firstVeryLongListItem secondVeryLongListItem thirdVeryLongListItem
			fourthVeryLongListItem
	);
}

```
